{"word":"Mary","slug":"mary","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mary</b> - <b>(a) Mother of Jesus,</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=16'>Mat 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=27'>Luk 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=38'>Luk 1:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=46'>Luk 1:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=56'>Luk 1:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=5'>Luk 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=16'>Luk 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=19'>Luk 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=34'>Luk 2:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=11'>Mat 2:11</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=43'>Luk 2:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=48'>Luk 2:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=46'>Mat 12:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=55'>Mat 13:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=1'>Joh 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=5'>Joh 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=12'>Joh 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=25'>Joh 19:25</a><p/>-- Characteristics of<p/>-- Submission<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=38'>Lu 1:38</a><p/>-- Faith and piety<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=46'>Lu 1:46-55</a><p/>-- Spiritual mindedness<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&vers